---
title: Sage Butter Pork with roasted aubergine and sweet potato mash
description: Herbaceous sage butter smothers the tender fried pork in this recipe. The super creamy sweet potato mash and roasted aubergine make this quick and tasty meal a shoo-in for family favourite this week.
